                        <path d="M7 14c-1.66 0-3-1.34-3-3 0-1.31.84-2.41 2-2.83V6.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h1a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v1.67c1.16.42 2 1.52 2 2.83 0 1.66-1.34 3-3 3zM21 6H11v2h10V6zM21 14H11v2h10v-2z"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <div class="flex-1">
